.nf
.sp .5
xdrrec_eof(xdrs)
\s-1XDR\s0 *xdrs;
int empty;
.fi
.ft R
.IP
This routine can be invoked only on
streams created by
.BR xdrrec_create(\|) .
After consuming the rest of the current record in the stream,
this routine returns one if the stream has no more input,
zero otherwise.
.br
.if t .ne 3
.LP
